
Final Year Project Topic: Self-taught a new language.(Node.js)
HTML/CSS/JAVASCRIPT/NODE.JS, Visual Studio tool, MySQL database, Bootstrap UI. 
Created a pizza ordering website, use CRUD(RESTful API) to keep track customer info and order info. 
Designed unique style website by using CSS and some Bootstrap example. 
MySQL have more than 3entities which are Customer,Pizza,Order,History,Payment. 
The website also contains registration and login functionality with authentication checks. 
The website does not allow customers to place orders unless they log into an existing account or sign up for a new account.
